						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab lying near the village Chāvaḍi.</hi></p>						

						<p>This record in characters of the <hi rend="bold">16th century A.D.</hi> states that a certain person (name lost) built a rest house <hi rend="italic">(dharma-śāle)</hi> in <hi rend="bold">Moina-Benndr</hi> (Modern Mōṭebennur). It is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Durmukhi, Jyeshha Śu. 6.</hi> The Śaka year is not given.</p>						

